---
// FAQ.astro - FAQ section with accordion and animated shapes
---

<section class="section faq reveal" id="faq" aria-label="The usual suspects">
  <div class="faq-shapes" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="faq-shape"></div>
    <div class="faq-shape"></div>
    <div class="faq-shape"></div>
  </div>
  <span class="section-label mono text-terracota">
    FAQ
  </span>
  <h2 class="section-title">The usual <span class="text-terracota">suspects</span></h2>
  <div class="glass-card">
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          What if I don't like it?
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" class="faq-chevron"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We work until you love it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          Can I update it later?
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" class="faq-chevron"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. Basic changes we'll teach you. Big stuff, we talk.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          What do you need from me to start?
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" class="faq-chevron"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Tell me about your business. Got a logo, photos, colors? Even better. If not, we create them together.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
